Title: IRONMAN 70.3 Power Slope
WorkoutDescription: Warm Up: 5 mins in Z1-2, 5 x (15 secs in Z3, 15 secs Z1-2, 15 secs in Z4, 15 secs in Z1-2) 5 mins in Z2. Main Set: 1 x (12 mins in Z3 + 8 mins in Z4), 4 mins recovery in Z1-2, 1 x (8 mins in Z3 + 5 mins in Z4), 3 mins recovery in Z1-2, 1 x (5 mins in Z3 + 3 mins in Z4), 2 mins recovery in Z1-2. Warm down. 5 mins in Z1-2.

Title: Race Practice Ride
WorkoutDescription: Warm Up: 30 mins in Z2. Main Set: 8 x (10 mins in Z3 + 5 mins in Z2). Warm Down: 30 mins in Z1-2.
CoachComments: This ride is designed to simulate race day, including efforts at race pace with short recoveries. You will benefit both psychologically and physiologically from this ride.
